@{LINDENT 0}
@{JCENTER} Beta Info

@{JLEFT}
@{LINDENT 2}

This  PatchCX  version  is  a  Beta Version, i.e. it was tested so far only by
myself  and  it might crash on your system, allthough it runs without problems
here.  For  that  reason  it  is  compiled with a run-time system which should
prevent crashes but also might not.


Therefore  the  PatchCX  binary  is quite big. Without the run-time system the
binary  is  about ~30 KByte smaller. Not really small either but, come on, all
the gui stuff need some bytes too....




@ENDNODE
